rl=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indy100.com%2Farticle%2Fscientist-looked-through-63-studies-conclude-atheists-more-intelligent-religious-people-metanalysis-7733926&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=52a4f91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.indy100.com/article/scientist-looked-through-63-studies-conclude-atheists-more-intelligent-religious-people-metanalysis-7733926</a><br />\n<br />\n你咁睇 Nyborg (2009)個study 做左3700人 (其實多數做幾百only), 搵到話係-0.05 經係根本就冇關...<br />\n咁你又唔講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766c44338174c21296c908bbd606535871139063","tid":250305,"uid":23115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇左篇journal<br />\n個meta analysis由60s既study到10s既study都有<br />\n有些少問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 2000打後既study其實好少<br />\n2. 2000打後個d個effect size其實好低 (-0.15已經係最多)<br />\n<br />\n所以根本冇correlation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係d media亂咁interpret<br />\non9當有趣</blockquote><br />\n就算analysis無問題, 極其量都係correlational study<br />\n無講到原因或者個因果mechanism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢用得 r 做effect size, 就擺明係個correlation only,<br />\n但連correlation都冇架其情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a39ce00d833e40084242eaf80e0572dbbda193","tid":250305,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"覺得神係善良果班先係最on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbee424407eb0ad7932359f8db7edd0cd43358d8","tid":250305,"uid":85190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:18:06.000Z","msg":"信自己 唔信神 都係一種信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid